item.title: streamflow time-series models
item.description: I discuss my major project on using deep learning for prediction of streamflow of nethravathi stream of kaveri river, India.

item.title: what's my 'why'?
item.description: I ponder: what is the ‘why’ of my life. i ponder upon my ‘why’, the reason to be and not to be, the reason to do and what to do with my life. Every now & then I have an existential crisis where I dig deep because all answers lie within.
